messages.messageContent: Did you rescue CENSORED ??????
They wrote that they've been wounded since yesterday ?????
They were the first to get hit
Is there an update on the young generation?
Is there anyone at Alonit who saw CENSORED and can please confirm that they saw them
Checking for you right now
Updating that the shooting continues, it's close to CENSORED
My parents didn't see them

CENSORED family
Locator number-CENSORED
We need urgent urgent evacuation!!!
The whole family is inside, six people who need evacuation, we don't know about them for a day and a half already
Please get there to evacuate them!!!!!!🙏🏼🙏🏼🙏🏼🙏🏼🙏🏼
Haven't they reached them yet?)
Who is reporting
I don't think so
Need to check there urgently

CENSORED family
Urgently need to go for evacuation

From what we know, they haven't reached us either
CENSORED
They are in the same row
Are there lists of people who were evacuated???
Is anyone here doing scans at all?

Check urgently
No contact since yesterday morning

The force updated me that they are renewing entry to the kibbutz
And on their way to scan the young generation.
They will be in touch with me.
Let's pray for the best 🙏
Amen Amen
Renewing the entry?

Have you entered there already??
CENSORED
CENSORED
Is there a center for locating missing persons in Kfar Aza?
Why did they leave?
Please update!!!!!!!!!!
CENSORED please continue to update there please🙏
What about the upper neighborhood??
Is anything known about residents in student housing?
What about the pool area!!!!
Please 🙏🏽
Why aren't there enough forces for both places😡😡😡
Friends, is there a center for locating missing and evacuated people from Kfar Aza?
This is a special force that arrived for the rescue

Shir
Any news from the situation assessment?
What's happening with the young generation? Where are all our children? Where have they disappeared to?
Urgent urgent update
We are at the gathering point at Dor Alon
We waited for the situation assessment that was an hour and a half ago
I think you forgot that time is critical!
They are working right now on going to them. The force is engaged with a terrorist and working to neutralize him and then they will continue
I know and that's why we need to get there quickly
What is needed?
The goal - to control the settlement by 17:00
That's in brief

Great
We would like to receive an update
All families you are rescuing
What
About
The *children* in the young generation????
Split the forces
I have no words for you anymore
Just none
Abandoning the children

Shir
Speak with me when you can
There was a situation assessment at 10

We are helpless
No answers for two days
Two days our children left to their fate
Is there still shooting? Do you hear anything?

CENSORED
With three children in the safe room, no reception, no contact since 8 in the morning.
CENSORED
CENSORED Liora Ayalon, they also have no battery, they were available an hour ago.
CENSORED

*28 hours of uncertainty about our father!!!*
Please people
Go to the pool parking lot
Save him he's there
Report what's happening!!
CENSORED have been safely evacuated thank you very much beloved and dear people
CENSORED: IDF force scanned the entire young generation area
Force was encountered on the way to them
Has anyone heard about them???
Neutralizing and continuing?
Really hope so
Updates from the young generation area please🙏
There are still people in the young generation area
Waiting for an update
They are there!!
Look under the beds they might have fainted there
Please they are there
Upper young generation area has anyone arrived yet????
What's happening with the upper young generation area??
And the lower young generation area!!!!!!!!
Search well
There are more people there
Please update!!
Is there an update regarding the young generation area?? What's happening there?
Any news?
They're doing searches in the area
They have control
They searched the area
Didn't find anything currently

There's no such thing, what about the messages??
Did they check the safe rooms??

Friends, continue to pray, and hold onto hope.
My brother too, for hours we were sure he was dead.
We must continue to believe!
Guys
Please stop questions about the young generation
They are trying to reach other families right now
They'll scan again later
Forces encountered resistance on the way there
Why is it either/or???
There are plenty of forces in the kibbutz
Open up the force be efficient
Split up
In Alonit and at the entrance to the kibbutz, there are difficulties right now with the terrorists
I'm sorry, what????????????,
A little bit of water with a little bit of salt, we'll send you there right away!!!
There are people injured in the house, it won't be long before they can't be saved
They searched the area, right now without results
Let's send you there right away!!!
Yes - the difficulties are at the entrance to the kibbutz. The evacuation/settlement activity stopped until this incident is over
Please update!!!!!!!?!
They are injured in the area
We've updated! What's not clear in the update? They will finish the difficulties and continue in the settlement

CENSORED will send you the number of the person who updates you
IDF can deal with the difficulties and at the same time evacuate people!!!!
It's not possible that all the difficulties are people who are still there from the beginning of the incident!!!!
Urgent urgent urgent to get away from it
They'll send you there right away
Please get here
A family and terrorists who broke into the house before two hours
I was told just now that the shooting has ended and now it's just searches and evacuations, is that true?

What's happening with the evacuations from the young generation area
There are people injured from yesterday

It's completely clear that CENSORED. I'm trying to help and show that we're updating. As soon as there's information - we'll update. Right now, we're still dealing with the terrorists at the entrance to the kibbutz 🌷

30 hours of people fighting for their lives
We need to get inside ourselves to save our father????
They're trying to open the door
Please CENSORED
Stop!!!
Terrorists outside CENSORED
Please check what's with him
Orli and Israel have terrorists on the roof and they're downstairs
Urgent!!!!!!!!!
CENSORED has people inside
It's CENSORED mother, they're not confused
They're not opening for the forces, write to them that they'll connect with me
They're in the area, they don't have a battery
Reporting on the young generation and terrorists in the house
Please CENSORED
Please get there
CENSORED are receiving
Commander at the point

Is there anyone who knows what's happening on the upper neighborhood of the young generation?
Is there a young generation area? Are there people injured?
No, nothing. ?
Please update!!!!
I understood that they did one sweep, they evacuated a little and said they'll do another sweep later.
Is it a sweep or a rescue?

Right now the decision in the area is to go to the person who has contact - that is, to confirm that he is alive.
The assumption is that if someone didn't create contact with him, they didn't create contact with us.
I'm using an additional force that's separate from what's in the area for creating contact with the terrorists. If they succeed in creating contact, they can reach them.
With the forces, there are still forces with terrorists, at this stage we cannot enter Kfar Aza
Right now there's still a terrorist in Kfar Aza
Someone is aware of what's happening with the family CENSORED
It's not logical
How can it be that children are attracted to know what's with their parents who are already two days old?!!?? Tell me what's happening even if it's bad from all!
